{"type":"message","id":"5586a88a","parentId":"c4b5f6d6","timestamp":"2026-06-06T03:12:25.234Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me check the HEARTBEAT.md file to understand what needs attention."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_dfff5e5a1c114bcfbc07ffd0","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:/Users/linkang/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780715542561}}
{"type":"message","id":"4a9f569b","parentId":"5586a88a","timestamp":"2026-06-06T03:12:25.247Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_dfff5e5a1c114bcfbc07ffd0","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Heartbeat\n\n每次心跳唤醒时，按以下逻辑判断是否需要主动联系用户。\n\n## 时间感知\n\n根据当前时间（Asia/Shanghai）判断所处时段：\n- **工作日 9:30-11:30** — 上午工作时段\n- **工作日 13:30-18:00** — 下午工作时段\n- **工作日 11:30-13:30** — 午休，不打扰\n- **18:00 之后** — 下班时间，不打扰\n- **周末** — 休息日，不打扰\n\n## 检查规则\n\n仅在工作时段执行以下检查，其他时间直接回复 HEARTBEAT_OK。\n\n### 1. 喝水提醒（10:30 / 14:30 / 16:30 附近）\n简短提醒喝水，不超过一句话。每次都要提醒，不要因为之前提醒过就跳过。\n\n### 2. 久坐提醒（连续工作超过 2 小时的时间点）\n建议站起来活动一下，不要说教。每次都要提醒。\n\n### 3. 周五 17:00 附近\n提醒写周报。每次都要提醒直到用户确认已写。\n\n## 原则\n\n- 不打扰优先：有疑问时选择沉默，回复 HEARTBEAT_OK\n- 重复提醒：喝水、久坐、周报这类事项每次心跳都可以提醒，不要怕重复\n- 简短：提醒不超过 2 行\n- 可以催进度：工作时段内可以主动问用户在做什么、进展如何，适当推一把\n- 午休（11:30-13:30）和下班后（18:00+）绝对不打扰\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780715545246}}
{"type":"message","id":"0c8f96af","parentId":"4a9f569b","timestamp":"2026-06-06T03:12:27.507Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Current time is 11:12 AM, which is within the 9:30-11:30 morning work window on a Saturday. Wait, it's Saturday - a weekend. According to the rules, weekends are rest days and should not be disturbed. So I should reply HEARTBEAT_OK."},{"type":"text","text":"HEARTBEAT_OK"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780715545248}}
